图片来源：视觉中国“ 云南临沧“强制师生服用大锅药方可入学”的规定被紧急叫停。
Source: Visual China's "Yunnan Lancang" forced teachers and students to take large pot prescription can be admitted to school "was urgently stopped.
2005年，云南曾出现“大锅药”医疗事故。
In 2005, there was a "big pot medicine" medical accident in Yunnan.
”2020年3月2日凌晨3时许，云南省临沧市教育体育局紧急制止大锅药事件。
On March 2, 2020, at about 3 a.m., the Lincang City Education and Sports Bureau in Yunnan Province urgently stopped the big pot medicine incident.
临沧市教育体育局发布的“关于临沧市学校师生服用‘大锅药’情况通报”称，个别县（区）教育体育局、市直学校存在要求通过上传购药证明、服药图片、视频等方式强制师生服用“大锅药”的错误，要求全市各级各类学校必须坚持自愿服用原则，杜绝强制师生服用“大锅药”，不得以是否服用“大锅药”作为春季学期开学报到入学条件。
The Education and Sports Bureau of Lincang City issued the "information circular on the use of 'big pot medicine' by teachers and students in schools in Linchang City," said that individual county (district) education and sports bureaus and city schools require teachers and students to take "big pot medicine" by uploading medicine certificates, pictures and videos.
对给师生家长带来不便和在社会上造成不良影响，“情况通报”里“深表歉意，深刻检讨”。
"I apologize for the inconvenience caused to the parents of teachers and students and the negative impact on the community," said the briefing "deeply regret, profound review.
目前，临沧市已要求各县(区)教育体育局、市直各学校立即停止执行原发通知。
At present, Lincang City has requested the county (district) education and sports bureau, municipal straight schools immediately stop the implementation of the original notice.
并要求各级各类学校必须坚持自愿服用原则，杜绝采取上传购药证明、服药图片、视频等方式强制师生服用“大锅药”，不得以是否服用“大锅药”作为春季学期开学报到入学条件；学校与卫健部门要密切配合，指导师生科学服用“大锅药”；师生在服药前要认真阅读临沧市中医医院(佤医医院)提供的《春季中医药预防指导方案》，知晓服药禁忌，确保用药安全。
Schools of all levels and types must adhere to the principle of voluntary dosing, prohibit teachers and students from taking "big pot medicine" by uploading drug purchase certificates, pictures and videos, and cooperate closely with teachers and health authorities to guide them to take the "big pot medicine."
临沧市临翔区教体局曾于2月29日下发通知，要求区直属学校及幼儿园的学生家长，自行购药并上传喝药照片。
The Lingxiang District Education and Sports Bureau issued a notice on February 29, asking parents of students in schools and kindergartens under the district to buy their own medicines and upload photos of drinking drugs.
当地部分药店出现抢购潮。
Some local pharmacies rush into the market.
3月1日，一份落款为临沧市临翔区教体局的《临沧市临翔区教育体育局关于报送2020年春季开学前服用大锅药情况的通知》在网络流传。
On March 1, a notice from Lingxiang District Education and Sports Bureau of Lincang City, which was signed by the Lingxiang District Education and Sports Bureau of Lincang City, was circulated online on March 1.
文件要求“各乡（镇、街道）教育办公室、区直各校（园）、各民办幼儿园”，“充分发挥中医药‘治未病’作用，要求所有学生都要服用大锅药，开学前由家长购买（上传喝药照片）。
The document calls for township (town, street) education offices, district schools (gardens) and private kindergartens to give full play to the role of TCM in "curing the disease," requiring all students to take large pot of medicine, which should be purchased by parents before the start of school (uploading photos of drinking medicine).
”要求各单位，从3月1日起，每日下午6时前，将本日服用“大锅药”的情况，以电子统计表形式上报区教体局安全股。
Units are required to report the use of "big pot medicine" to the District Sports Bureau's Safety Unit in the form of electronic statistical tables by 6 p.m. daily from March 1.
2月29日15时，在国务院联防联控机制在北京举行新闻发布会，北京地坛医院中西医结合科主任医师王融冰在发布会上表示，中药方剂主要是用来治疗有症状的人，不主张没有症状的健康人使用中成药来预防新冠肺炎，（盲目使用）没有意义。
At 1500 hours on February 29, at a press conference held in Beijing by the State Council's Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism, Wang Rongbing, chief physician of the Department of Chinese Medicine and Western Medicine of Beijing Ditan Hospital, said at the press conference.
预防还是要按照联防联控的要求，做好个人防护，不到疫区去、不参加聚会、戴好口罩、做好手卫生，保护好自己、家人和周围工作的同事，这样才能起到真正的预防作用。
Prevention or in accordance with the requirements of the Joint Prevention Control, do a good job of personal protection, do not go to epidemic areas, do not attend meetings, wear masks, do good hand hygiene, and protect themselves, their families and colleagues working around them, so as to have a real preventive effect.
2005年，云南曾出现“大锅药”医疗事故。
In 2005, there was a "big pot medicine" medical accident in Yunnan.
据生活新报报道，2005年6月15日下午2时左右，云南省昆明市禄劝彝族苗族自治县茂山乡红石岩小学为预防发生水痘，集体服用大锅药，服药后陆续有学生出现腹痛、腹泻、恶心、呕吐头痛等中毒症状，其中一名学生症状严重，经县医院抢救无效死亡。
On June 15, 2005, at about 2: 00 p.m., Rushiyan Primary School in Maomao Township, Miao Autonomous County, Kunming, Yunnan Province, took large-scale medicine to prevent the occurrence of chickenpox. Students developed symptoms such as abdominal pain, diarrhea, nausea and vomiting headache.
这次一共有153人因饮用了“大锅中药”后中毒，其中有151人是红石岩小学的学生，另外2人分别是学生家长和学校老师。
A total of 153 people were poisoned after drinking a cauldron of traditional Chinese medicine, 151 of whom were students at the primary school and two were parents and school teachers.
